description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to recap the Patriots shutout victory over the Jets on Monday Night Football (1:00). The guys dissect a horrific performance from Sam Darnold, New England's stellar defense and Tom Brady's future. Next, a roundup of news from the league (31:00) and forecasting the AFC Playoff Picture (37:30).
